PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Transport of Ronald E. Lawless, of Beaconsfield, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian National Railway Company for a term of five months; and re-appointment of the said Ronald E. Lawless as President and Chief Executive Officer of the said Company to hold office during pleasure for a term ending July 1, 1992, effective April 1, 1992.

precis:
